    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD hemolysis model provides sufficient confidence for regulatory submission. Monte Carlo UQ demonstrates hemolysis predictions remain below the clinical threshold across the operating envelope. Residual gaps in discretization error and model-form uncertainty are considered acceptable given the conservative nature of the power-law model. Medium assurance level declared.",
